# folding at home playbook

## Scope

This is a simple playbook to deploy the Folding at Home binary
and run to give _idle_ CPU cycles to the project.

### Supported OSs

- CentOS 8

## Usage

1. Copy this repository onto your machine
2. Confirm `ansible` is installed

```bash
sudo dnf install python3
sudo dnf install python3-pip
pip3 install ansible --user
```
3. Go into the directory and run

```bash
ansible-playbook --connection=local playbook.yml
```

## Testing

There is a [Vagrantfile](./Vagrantfile) in this repository. You can
test this via:

```bash
vagrant up --provision
```

